item.title: CVE-2021-21421|2024-08-03T18:09:16.150Z -- creharmony -- node-etsy-client
item.description: node-etsy-client is a NodeJs Etsy ReST API Client. Applications that are using node-etsy-client and reporting client error to the end user will offer api key value too This is fixed in node-etsy-client v0.3.0 and later.
